data.description: Come check out this cute newly sided home! 5 bedroom, 2 bathroom, storage room and laundry area. LVP flooring throughout the kitchen, living room, hallway and bathroom upstairs. Newly installed pellet stove upstairs and a wood burning stove downstairs, and more storage room underneath the stairs. This home sits on 1.19 acres with a fenced in field for all your animals and a approx. 12x12 shelter. 2 water shares included!  Enjoy a three-door shop approximately 30 x 15 to store your toys, equipment, wood or anything else and a smaller shed right next to it for more storage space. This cute home is a must see. Buyer to verify square ft.
